---
import BaseHead from '../../components/BaseHead.astro';
---
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <BaseHead title="Ergonomics: Comfortable Setup & Peripherals - LaptopVette" description="Best practices for ergonomic laptop use, including posture, accessories, and recommended keyboards and mice." path="/guides/ergonomics" type="article" />
</head>
<body>

  <nav class="navbar">
    <div class="container"><a href="/" class="logo">Laptop<span>Vette</span></a></div>
  </nav>

  <article class="article-container">
    <h1>Ergonomics: Comfortable Laptop Use and Recommended Peripherals</h1>
    <p>Long-term comfort and reducing strain depend on setup and peripherals. Laptops are inherently compact, so adding the right accessories and following posture best practices makes a big difference.</p>

    <section>
      <h2>Basic Setup Tips</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Raise the screen so the top third of the display is at eye level using a stand.</li>
        <li>Use an external keyboard and mouse to keep wrists neutral and shoulders relaxed.</li>
        <li>Keep the laptop at a comfortable distance (roughly an arm's length) from your eyes.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Recommended Peripherals</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Ergonomic keyboards with negative tilt or tenting options to reduce wrist extension.</li>
        <li>Vertical or sculpted mice that reduce pronation and wrist strain.</li>
        <li>Adjustable laptop stands and external monitors for multi-screen setups.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Accessories For Students & Home Offices</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Portable lap desks for flexible posture when working on the couch.</li>
        <li>Lightweight external keyboards for longer typing sessions.</li>
        <li>Bluetooth mice with good battery life for mobility.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <p style="margin-top:20px;">Want specific model suggestions? I can recommend ergonomic keyboards and mice at different price points and link to current pricing.</p>
  </article>

  <style>
    * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    body { font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; background-color: #f8fafc; color: #0f172a; line-height: 1.85; }
    .container { max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 20px; }
    
    /* Navigation */
    .navbar { background: #ffffff; border-bottom: 1px solid #d1d5db; position: sticky; top: 0; z-index: 100; }
    .navbar .container { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; height: 70px; }
    .logo { font-size: 24px; font-weight: 700; color: #0f172a; text-decoration: none; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: -0.5px; }
    .logo span { color: #b91c1c; }
    
    /* Article Container */
    .article-container { max-width: 1064px; margin: 40px auto; padding: 40px; background: #ffffff; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; border-radius: 12px; }
    .article-container h1 { font-size: 32px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.25; color: #0f172a; }
    .article-container > p { margin-bottom: 1.4em; line-height: 1.85; text-align: justify; }
    .article-container h2 { font-size: 22px; margin: 56px 0 22px 0; border-left: 4px solid #b91c1c; padding-left: 15px; }
    .article-container section { margin-bottom: 2em; }
    .article-container ul { list-style: disc inside; }
    .article-container li { margin-bottom: 12px; line-height: 1.6; }
  </style>
</body>
</html>
